dublin_core.dcvalue: mHealth Alliance Publication The objective of this paper is to review existing mHealth interventions and successful approaches applications as well as identify gaps in knowledge for the use of mHealth in neonatal resuscitation It was prepared for the United Nations Commission on Life Saving Commodities Neonatal Resuscitation Technical Reference Team March 2014
mHealth and Neonatal Resuscitation: A Review of Interventions, Approaches and Applications
